                            <comment id="20595" author="hudson" created="Mon, 3 Oct 2011 08:48:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in &lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/images/16x16/red.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b1_8/./arch=i686,build_type=client,distro=el5,ib_stack=ofa/131/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;lustre-b1_8 &#187; i686,client,el5,ofa #131&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-146&quot; title=&quot;executable files on NFS share failed with &amp;quot;Text file busy&amp;quot; when executed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-146&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-146&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; mds_open() may deadlock&lt;/p&gt;

